%N A397427 Decimal expansion of Sum_{p prime} p/((p+1)*(p^3-1)).
%C A397427 The constant c in the formula Sum_{a,b <= x} Omega(f(a,b)) = c * x^2 + O(x*log(x)^4), where Omega = A001222, and f(a, b) = gcd(ab, a + b)/gcd(a, b) (Tóth, 2026, p. 4, Corollary 5).
%H A397427 László Tóth, <a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/2606.20057">On the asymptotic density of the ordered pairs (a, b) of positive integers such that gcd(ab, a + b) = gcd(a, b)</a>, arXiv:2606.20057 [math.NT], 2026.
%F A397427 Equals Sum_{k>=3} A115360(k-3)*P(k) = Sum_{k>=0, j=3..5} (-1)^(j+1) * P(6*k+j), where P is the prime zeta function.
%e A397427 0.135052634083685867172376680676434910097664043844249...
%t A397427 With[{m = 120}, RealDigits[Sum[(-1)^(j+1) * PrimeZetaP[6*k+j], {j, 3, 5}, {k, 0, m}], 10, m][[1]]]
%o A397427 (PARI) sumeulerrat(p/((p+1)*(p^3-1)))
%Y A397427 Cf. A001222, A115360.
%Y A397427 Cf. A065465, A065466, A065468, A065486, A382562.
